videos.description: Duke's Tre Jones dribbles out of trouble, then pulls up from mid-range and connects on the jump shot.
videos.headline: Jones sinks smooth pull-up jumper

videos.description: Duke's Alex O'Connell knocks down a contested 3-pointer and it gets the fans at Cameron Indoor Stadium on their feet.

videos.description: Duke's Cassius Stanley crosses his defender to get into the lane then connects on the floater through contact for the score.

videos.description: Duke's Jack White collides with a fellow Blue Devil and stays on the floor for several moments before finally walking off the court.

videos.description: Tre Jones splits two defenders with a bounce pass to find the cutting Matthew Hurt who rises up for the two-handed slam.
